{"tid":2163414,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[香城文化局]集思廣益 — 邀請各位巴絲一齊編寫我城歷史","createTime":"2020-08-18T15:53:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-26T15:29:49.000Z","uid":52152,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c33650bf2bb115bb617a3d3b71b6df75b5a3d30d","tid":2163414,"uid":52152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T15:53:17.000Z","msg":"經過上一個post 之後，發現連登真係有好多深藏不露既巴絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n簡單講返我哋做緊啲咩先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />　我哋依家係度砌曬個整體既時間線，有左個初步既大綱之後就慢慢填返上文下理。但係發現就算依家工作小組入面既人都未必可以完全包括曬我城既所有歷史<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />尤其係依家要同時間競賽，要係所有歷史記錄未被改寫之前完成<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以決定集思廣益推出實驗性既企劃，由連登敢多位巴絲去參與編寫我城既歷史。<br />\n如果巴絲有興趣一齊編寫既話，可以填下面既form<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/7vuxZWWzZQnD1KoZA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2F7vuxZWWzZQnD1KoZA&d=%2BN%2BzEUDrQz9IsHzLxo0c5vGl%2B26pDsgLotMYn9d4AWI%3D&h=1db4ea73\" target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/7vuxZWWzZQnD1KoZA</a><br />\n<br />\n入面好粗略敢分左3個時段，由<span class=\"red\">４個大範疇（政制(司法／行政／立法）、經濟結構、當時生活環境、社會狀況）</span>去講。內容長短不限，可以簡單一句又得，一段講曬來龍去脈都歡迎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />最好有年份＋事件方便我咃歸類同查證。<br />\n例如：<br />\n政制方面：<em>1843年 - 香港殖民地憲章頒布</em>／<em>1843年 - 香港殖民地憲章頒布同時委任砵典乍為首任港督</em><br />\n收集完大家既意見之後，我哋都會拎黎參考並盡可能作出查證。如果有啲內容係冇辦法由第三方作出查證既話，我哋會聯絡返果位朋友再提供資料／出post拎出黎大家討論。<br />\n由於依個係實驗性既企劃，我哋會定期檢討同改善。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e32b720df749a825447af3c0b59cc685956f6f3e","tid":2163414,"uid":37577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T19:47:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3c223864db0dfe7061035d6930901260b51d8c02","tid":2163414,"uid":56311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T19:55:49.000Z","msg":"咁早呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c189a92234b99c23865c6e24cf72796f2f4c306","tid":2163414,"uid":120064,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T23:21:06.000Z","msg":"要寫香港史點解唔直接去搵相關學者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\ne.g.蕭國健"},{"pid":"340df7fa0ce3e825d261827ac973d8b3c2e9917d","tid":2163414,"uid":27650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c189a92234b99c23865c6e24cf72796f2f4c306","tid":2163414,"uid":120064,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T23:21:06.000Z","msg":"要寫香港史點解唔直接去搵相關學者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\ne.g.蕭國健"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T00:00:17.000Z","msg":"本地有好多香港史專家都係幫政權背書，同埋史觀同樓主果種好唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3182ec6749686e21912c7ddd274ef3b99ff33d10","tid":2163414,"uid":27650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T00:06:03.000Z","msg":"btw晏少少再抽時間寫啲嘢，夜訓早醒所以有啲累<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16aa22cb14741c4312bc30f33baa17d00914dc27","tid":2163414,"uid":52152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"340df7fa0ce3e825d261827ac973d8b3c2e9917d","tid":2163414,"uid":27650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c189a92234b99c23865c6e24cf72796f2f4c306","tid":2163414,"uid":120064,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T23:21:06.000Z","msg":"要寫香港史點解唔直接去搵相關學者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\ne.g.蕭國健"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T00:00:17.000Z","msg":"本地有好多香港史專家都係幫政權背書，同埋史觀同樓主果種好唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T12:06:52.000